The pod's occupant finally smashes his way out ... he turns out to be 
an oversized jack-o-lantern with eight vines, rather like a land-
bound octopus.  (He's an octolantern, a creature native to the same 
world Yggdrasil Prime got his beast mode.)

"HAHAHAHA!  I'm free at last!  Heehee!"  This is not evil or crazed 
laughter; he's actually somehow amused by the sudden breathing room.  
The bizzarre Maximal begins an odd dance as he celebrates his escape.
